                formularios de contacto.
              </span></span
            >
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start space-x-3 rtl:space-x-reverse">
            <svg
              class="flex-shrink-0 w-[10px] h-[10px] sm:w-3.5 sm:h-3.5 text-green-500 mt-[2px] sm:mt-1"
              aria-hidden="true"
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 16 12"
            >
              <path
                stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M1 5.917 5.724 10.5 15 1.5"></path>
            </svg>
            <span
              ><span class="font-semibold text-gray-900">
                Automatizar la gestión de contenido
              </span> mediante archivos JSON.</span
            >
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start space-x-3 rtl:space-x-reverse">
            <svg
              class="flex-shrink-0 w-[10px] h-[10px] sm:w-3.5 sm:h-3.5 text-green-500 mt-[2px] sm:mt-1"
              aria-hidden="true"
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 16 12"
            >
              <path
                stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M1 5.917 5.724 10.5 15 1.5"></path>
            </svg>
            <span
              ><span class="font-semibold text-gray-900">
                Optimizar el rendimiento
              </span> de la web, obteniendo una <span
                class="font-semibold text-gray-900"
              >
                mejora del 23.4%.
              </span></span
            >
          </li>
        </ul>
        <h5 class="text-sm sm:text-base lg:text-lg font-medium">
          Habilidades desarrolladas:
        </h5>
        <ul
          class="flex justify-center sm:justify-normal flex-wrap gap-3 sm:gap-5"
        >
          <li
            class="rounded-full border px-2.5 py-0.5 text-xs font-semibold transition-colors border-transparent bg-[#F4F4F5]"
          >
            Astro
          </li>
          <li
            class="rounded-full border px-2.5 py-0.5 text-xs font-semibold transition-colors border-transparent bg-[#F4F4F5]"
          >
            JavaScript
          </li>
          <li
            class="rounded-full border px-2.5 py-0.5 text-xs font-semibold transition-colors border-transparent bg-[#F4F4F5]"
          >
            React
          </li>
          <li
            class="rounded-full border px-2.5 py-0.5 text-xs font-semibold transition-colors border-transparent bg-[#F4F4F5]"
          >
            Tailwind
          </li>
          <li
            class="rounded-full border px-2.5 py-0.5 text-xs font-semibold transition-colors border-transparent bg-[#F4F4F5]"
          >
            SEO
          </li>
        </ul>
      </section>
      <img
        class="w-96 rounded-lg hidden lg:block"
        src="Nosotros.webp"
        alt="Foto de Pachamama Turismo"
      />
    </div>
  </article>
</section>
